The paper deals with the operation of forgetting in Answer Set Programming (ASP), which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Logic (LO). The paper also discusses the properties that operators should satisfy, which falls under the category of Programming Languages (PL). The paper's focus on practical issues and the presentation of a concrete operator suggests that it may also be relevant to Computational Linguistics (CL) and Cryptography and Security (CR), as forgetting is a crucial operation in both fields.
